OL,3,CPhysiotherapist in Guernsey sanctioned
OL,4,Cover data protection breach
OL,6,FGuernsey's Data Protection Authority
OL,7,F(ODPA) has sanctioned First Contact
OL,8,FHealth, after it failed to implement
OL,9,Fsufficient security measures to
OL,10,Fprevent a phishing attack.
OL,12,FThe cybersecurity breach saw
OL,13,Ffraudsters successfully target an
OL,14,Femployee's email account, gaining
OL,15,Faccess to confidential health data at
OL,16,Fthe physiotherapist.
OL,18,FFirst Contact Health reported the data
OL,19,Fprotection breach to the ODPA in May
OL,20,F2024 after realising it had occurred.
