OL,6,FThe ODPA then launched an inquiry into
OL,7,Fthe phishing attack, and found four
OL,8,Fkey failings in First Contact Health's
OL,9,Fcybersecurity measures.
OL,11,FFirst, multi-factor authentication was
OL,12,Fabsent from email logins, which left
OL,13,Fthe physiotherapist vulnerable to
OL,14,Fbrute-force attacks (where a
OL,15,Fcyberattacker uses trial-and-error
OL,16,Fwith password combinations to access
OL,17,Fan account).
