OL,6,FIn a statement, the ODPA said: "The
OL,7,FAuthority has found First Contact
OL,8,FHealth to have breached the Law and
OL,9,Fhas imposed an order requiring that it
OL,10,Ftake several steps to improve its
OL,11,Fsecurity safeguards.
OL,13,F"The Authority will be ensuring that
OL,14,Fthese steps are taken and can
OL,15,Fundertake further enforcement action
OL,16,Fshould this order not be complied with.
