OL,6,F"Health information is considered
OL,7,Fspecial category data, under the Law,
OL,8,Fand this increased sensitivity should
OL,9,Fbe borne in mind when considering
OL,10,Fsecurity safeguard measures."
OL,12,FIn response, First Contact Health
OL,13,Fclaims it undertook an internal
OL,14,Finvestigation, and has completed a
OL,15,F'comprehensive' upgrade of its
OL,16,Fcybersecurity.
