OL,6,FThe physiotherapist said: "We want to
OL,7,Freassure our patients that our primary
OL,8,FElectronic Medical Record (EMR)
OL,9,Fsystem`which stores the vast majority
OL,10,Fof patient files`was not breached. The
OL,11,Fincident involved very limited
OL,12,Finformation pertaining to a small
OL,13,Fnumber of patients.
OL,15,F"We have substantially upgraded our IT
OL,16,Finfrastructure to meet and exceed
OL,17,Fcurrent industry security standards,
OL,18,Fand have implemented a schedule for
OL,19,Fregular, rigorous security audits to
OL,20,Fstay ahead of emerging threats
